Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.72,2:03:34.91,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}蜉蝣飘舞于他的身旁
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.55,2:03:40.95,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不为人知 孑然一身
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.23,2:03:47.43,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他朝着远空飞翔
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.85,2:03:58.12,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}无所畏惧 飞舞升空
