Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.03,2:04:18.76,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他的生命就是那朵飞机云
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.76,2:04:32.15,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如今已无法得知
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.49,2:04:42.55,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他是否至死仍从窗户眺望那片蓝天
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.77,2:04:48.62,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}他人无法理解
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.36,2:04:54.77,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只叹息他英年早逝
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.07,2:05:05.22,CN_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}然而 他却是幸福的
